!X TB_Common_module
!X
!% TB module computes the tight-binding Hamiltonian matrix elements
!% in the two-center approximation, applying the general expressions
!% derived by A.V. Podolskiy and P. Vogl Phys. Rev. B {\bf 69}, 233101 (2004).
!X
